{"tid":550761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"理大學生會2號莊偽本土 真赤化by","createTime":"2018-02-05T05:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T04:51:03.000Z","uid":121241,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0f922ccf88a4447150c243b15958afb6c0761557","tid":550761,"uid":121241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"事源係論壇 聽到兩支莊比人問政治聯繫<br />\n除左理凝有民主黨intern evp<br />\n煥賢既財政 施子健 竟然幫過民建聯李慧琼助選<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1fa60ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我心諗 唔係掛 咁都搵佢做大莊財政？<br />\n愈諗愈唔對路 於是搵下資料<br />\n比我搵到佢去中聯辦實習團啲資料<br />\n個團係2017暑假 新鮮滖熱辣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130414_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130414_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1af2ef6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c921adc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個財政上年都選過大莊<br />\n最後支莊「被流選」<br />\n因為啲莊員比人鼓勵quit<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130452_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130452_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ee659f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後個財政再去中共交流團<br />\n今年再去選多次大莊？ 仲要扮本土咁岩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5de11990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢個P洪子健仲話佢係比屋企人迫去助選<br />\n迫？ 佢笑得咁開心<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130540_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130540_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0311ca03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有好多感想<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130605_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130605_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ddfb16d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130609_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130609_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e63fc4d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上得共青團微博 唔係中共屬意+自己人邊會上到？<br />\n根本純正紅色血統<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130627_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130627_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4fa73e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後尾再發現原來個財政張提名表格衰左<br />\n之後佢支莊話如果贏左一定會補選佢<br />\n嘩 避風頭唔使出ocon 之後再係評議會過會上 陰陰濕濕<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=604272e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130656_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130656_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=76fe3ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(上年4號莊煥理)<br />\n再發現原來煥賢個p + ivp<br />\n上年同個財政係同一支大莊<br />\n邊有可能個莊員去完中共交流團都唔知？<br />\n都唔知係有份共謀 定 天真無政治智慧<br />\n如果有份共謀 就成支莊誠信破產<br />\n如果天真無政治智慧 佢支莊都唔知仲有邊個係鬼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fd413113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗諗下其實個P洪子鍵都好有問題<br />\n上年4號莊話緊學校校董會高層個陣<br />\n煥賢個P (上年4號個個EVP) 竟然退選？<br />\n你唔夠膽定助攻呀？<br />\n<br />\n再講煥賢個IVP做評議會秘書個陣<br />\n唔跟程序亂收form 遲得好離譜都照收 <br />\n(可以問返評議會啲人)<br />\n為左討好啲soc 規則都唔跟 <br />\n再聽聞佢地想拎內地學生協會啲票 真心咩？<br />\n<br />\n公義？ 程序？你地同對家有咩分別？<br />\n點知你地係咪扮本土玩膠出賣poly人？<br />\n點知你地係咪鬼 之後穿su櫃桶？ <br />\n畢竟依加su好似有幾百萬儲備<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130756_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130756_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=31edca1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/130819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F130819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5b13cd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比個機會人啦！<br />\n too simple, sometimes naive<br />\n仲有資格上大莊？<br />\n一直比你地蒙在鼓裏<br />\n<br />\n#唔好學鄭若驊話自己政治敏感度不足<br />\n#信錯你地班人 <br />\n#真理愈辯愈明 <br />\n#allin2 #allin共匪 #allin弱智<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做過su打雜"},{"pid":"f0e60ebbcaacd470de13e8db37406330c96122ef","tid":550761,"uid":121241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f922ccf88a4447150c243b15958afb6c0761557","tid":550761,"uid":121241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"事源係論壇 聽到兩支莊比人問政治聯繫<br />\n除左理凝有民主黨intern evp<br />\n煥賢既財政 施子健 竟然幫過民建聯李慧琼助選<br 